&lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind --&gt;&lt;dependency&gt;    &lt;groupId&gt;com.fasterxml.jackson.core&lt;/groupId&gt;    &lt;artifactId&gt;jackson-databind&lt;/artifactId&gt;    &lt;version&gt;2.14.2&lt;/version&gt;&lt;/dependency&gt;
其次之前我们提到过了加上@ResponseBody注解之后，return单纯就是返回一个字符串而已，然后JSON中也同样会出现JSON乱码的问题，有2种解决方法，第一种是在RequestMapping处加东西：@RequestMapping(value = &quot;/json2&quot;,produces = &quot;text/html;charset=UTF-8&quot;)第二种则是修改springMvc的配置文件，一劳永逸：
&lt;mvc:annotation-driven&gt;    &lt;mvc:message-converters register-defaults=&quot;true&quot;&gt;        &lt;bean class=&quot;org.springframework.http.converter.StringHttpMessageConverter&quot;&gt;            &lt;property name=&quot;supportedMediaTypes&quot;&gt;                &lt;list&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;text/html;charset=UTF-8&lt;/value&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;application/json;charset=UTF-8&lt;/value&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;text/plain;charset=UTF-8&lt;/value&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;application/xml;charset=UTF-8&lt;/value&gt;                &lt;/list&gt;            &lt;/property&gt;        &lt;/bean&gt;    &lt;/mvc:message-converters&gt;&lt;/mvc:annotation-driven&gt;
